values.description: Hi Guys, thanks again for a great environment and a great competition.  The final docker image took a bit longer than expected to complete, so we are not sure if this submission will actually be accepted.  Along those lines, we fell with just a little more time a few key items that we were not able to finalize to would come together.  Would the organizers \(and if so, the other teams\) be interested in extending the submission window with something along the lines of an overall score penalty?  Either way, thanks again.
